{"tid":1366631,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[徵集Pokemon Go訓練員幫手做問卷]","createTime":"2019-07-26T04:14:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T04:39:32.000Z","uid":265480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b977a69faace2f9a615c8efb95be4fd12afedfe4","tid":1366631,"uid":265480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:14:06.000Z","msg":"P牌第一次出post。<br />\n戴定頭盔先，我都知響宜家呢個critical moment話要做功課好off topic，同埋都知連登應該唔多人玩Pokemon Go，不過數據仲未夠，即管試下呢度post。<br />\n<br />\n話說，小弟正在完成資訊管理碩士課程的畢業論文，題目是關於精靈寶可夢GO(google上似乎是這樣翻譯)玩家如何透過資訊分享和交換資訊，實現社會連結。當初諗題目，唔單只諗到Pokemon GO，仲諗到社交媒體/群組分享，都係因為覺得呢種AR Game影響下玩家們在fb上分享資訊、經驗，係一件好神奇既事。<br />\n<br />\n（BTW，連登一網絡上一要人，就即有人判斷是非，然後就即刻有人於現實地點出現，不問姓名就互相幫忙，呢個更加神奇。希望待香港光復後，會有人做正式研究。）<br />\n<br />\n研究涉及問卷調查，以下是中英文版問卷連結。我比較長氣，問題比較多，不過全部都係選擇題，十分鐘內會做完。如果大家唔嫌棄的話，希望可以完成問卷，並且send比身邊有玩Pokemon GO的朋友做。<br />\n<br />\n中文版﹕<a href=\"https://forms.gle/coJGCyYHmGg8V8FQ9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FcoJGCyYHmGg8V8FQ9&d=AixoiqhHuTrv0%2F0Xa%2FX9x%2BIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=358373db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/coJGCyYHmGg8V8FQ9</a><br />\n<br />\n英文版﹕<a href=\"https://forms.gle/EnBsAVd1AZ2JmVwj7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FEnBsAVd1AZ2JmVwj7&d=AixoiqhHuTrv0%2F0Xa%2FX9x%2BIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=34d9ae9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/EnBsAVd1AZ2JmVwj7</a><br />\n<br />\n最後，好人一生平安，多謝。🙏🙏🙏"},{"pid":"5351daf397e3a763adb0f551a4cc1f112de6e2dc","tid":1366631,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:19:06.000Z","msg":"J圖都冇叫人做問卷?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f29d8b45b80a25a25d42dbca2ea209cd8ef53b6","tid":1366631,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:25:38.